RFP Intelligence Copilot — Alembic migrations

Quick reference:
  alembic upgrade head              # apply all pending migrations
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add column x"   # generate new migration
  alembic downgrade -1              # roll back one migration
  alembic history                   # list migration history

The DATABASE_URL env var overrides the SQLite dev default in alembic.ini.
For production PostgreSQL:
  export DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://<user>:<pw>@<host>/<db>
  alembic upgrade head
